'''Domain Tsun''' was a [[Domain]] among the [[Warrior caste]] of the [[Yuuzhan Vong]]. During the [[Battle of Yuuzhan'tar]], the vessels of Domain Tsun were part of the flotilla sent to attack [[Zonama Sekot/Legends|Zonama Sekot]]. During the battle, [[Supreme Commander (Yuuzhan Vong rank)|Supreme Commander]] [[Sla Tsun]] was ordered to crash the domain's [[matalok]]s into Zonama Sekot.<ref name="TUF">''[[The New Jedi Order: The Unifying Force]]''</ref>

